OL,3,CMurder investigation after body found
OL,4,Cin Peak District
OL,6,FA murder investigation has been
OL,7,Flaunched after the death of a man in
OL,8,Fthe Peak District.
OL,10,FDerbyshire Police were called to
OL,11,Freports of a man's body being found at
OL,12,FNine Ladies Stone Circle in Stanton
OL,13,FLees at 1.38pm on Monday 22 June.
OL,15,FEmergency services attended the scene
OL,16,Fand a 26-year-old man was pronounced
OL,17,Fdead.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G1/5
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
