CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F341A1782278351
OL,3,CMurder investigation after body found
OL,4,Cin Peak District
OL,6,FThe man has not yet been formally
OL,7,Fidentified but police have said his
OL,8,Ffamily are aware and are being
OL,9,Fsupported by specialist officers.
OL,11,FAn investigation into the
OL,12,Fcircumstances of his death has been
OL,13,Flaunched.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G2/5
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,342,340,120,260,000,100
PN,34103
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F341A1782278351
OL,3,CMurder investigation after body found
OL,4,Cin Peak District
OL,6,FDetective Inspector Tony Owen, from
OL,7,Fthe East Midlands Special Operations
OL,8,FUnit, who is leading the
OL,9,Finvestigation, said: "We know that
OL,10,Fthere have been a lot of people in the
OL,11,Farea of Nine Ladies Stone Circle over
OL,12,Fthe weekend celebrating the summer
OL,13,Fsolstice and this incident will
OL,14,Fundoubtedly be shocking and
OL,15,Fdistressing to those who were present,
OL,16,Fas well as the wider community.
OL,26,@qD@VOU
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G3/5
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,342,340,120,260,000,100
PN,34104
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F341A1782278351
OL,3,CMurder investigation after body found
OL,4,Cin Peak District
OL,6,F"We are currently working to
OL,7,Funderstand the circumstances of this
OL,8,Fman's death so I would urge anyone who
OL,9,Fwas at the site over the weekend, as
OL,10,Fwell as anyone with any information,
OL,11,Fto please get in touch with us.
OL,13,F"We know people have been coming and
OL,14,Fgoing from the area over the course of
OL,15,Fthe weekend so it is vital that anyone
OL,16,Fwho was in attendance at any point
OL,17,Fover the weekend speaks to officers.
OL,26,@nD@AOUuD@AOU
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G4/5
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,342,340,120,260,000,100
PN,34105
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F341A1782278351
OL,3,CMurder investigation after body found
OL,4,Cin Peak District
OL,6,F"We know that this will be of concern
OL,7,Fto people and there will be an
OL,8,Fincreased police presence in the area
OL,9,Fover the coming days so I'd urge
OL,10,Fanyone with any concerns to please
OL,11,Fspeak to an officer."
OL,13,FOfficers are keen to hear from anyone
OL,14,Fwith any information as well as anyone
OL,15,Fwith dashcam footage from the area.
OL,26,@nD@AOUsD@UO]
